# ESP32 Water Level Monitoring (Basic)

A simple IoT project using ESP32 to monitor water levels and send data via MQTT.

## 🔧 Features
- Ultrasonic water level sensing
- WiFi connectivity
- MQTT data publishing
- Easy setup

## ⚡ Quick Start

1. Update WiFi + MQTT in `config.h`
2. Upload code to ESP32
3. Open Serial Monitor

## 📡 Output Example

{
  "level": 72.5
}

## 🧠 Use Cases
- Water tanks
- Agriculture monitoring
- Smart irrigation

## 🚀 Future Improvements
- Dashboard
- Alerts
- Cloud integration

